reviewText: So good for your mind and soul - Love It!

Movie was well done both the acting and the story. Very inspiring movie and a lot of drama. A lot of felling and thought went in to the production.
A very inspiring movie that was actually Inspired by a true story.  Not a predictable movie as many are but more like a real life drama.
You won't be sorry you purchased this one.
best movie i order i have watch this movie at least 20 times since i got it.
Deeply Inspiring. Moving, deep and emotional. Great movie.
